name: Jeffrey Dev
bio: Jeffrey graduated from General Assembly in 2022. Afterwords, he went on to work for PEAK6, a fintech company headquartered in Chicago, IL where he took his first step into his new chosen career path in Technology. In his role as a Finance Systems Analyst, he supported the Finance team by extracting, transforming, and loading data as well as writing scripts to automate their day-to-day tasks.
goals: Building off of the knowledge and experience he gained working at PEAK6, Jeffrey looks to take the next step towards becoming a Full-Time Software Engineer by joining the Emerging Talent Software Engineering program at JP Morgan.
